<p>
Charley wants to escape the stress of modern life and travel to Galesburg, Illinois, a peaceful town of the past. While attempting to buy tickets at the third level, the clerk refuses his modern currency. Confused, he leaves and later tells his friend Sam, a psychiatrist, about the discovery. Sam first considers the third level a psychological escape created by Charley’s mind. Later, Sam travels to the third level and confirms it exists, adding a mysterious twist to the story.
</p>

<div class="extra">
